This is the readme file.

To use nix* commands nix have to be pre-installed.
Nix can be installed by running
> curl install-nix | sh

To build application with nix
> nix-build --attr logAPI release.nix

To enter development environment
> nix-shell --attr logAPI.env release.nix

To build application and create docker tar archive
> nix-build --attr logAPI release.nix

To build with docker-compose:
> docker-compose build

To run application with docker-compose
> docker-compose up


